<subSubSection pageId="37" pageNumber="38" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,1268,1511]" box="[151,558,1268,1295]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,530,1268,1295]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Number of specimens recorded.</emphasis>
5.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,1268,1511]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1304,1331]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Distribution.</emphasis>
Europe, but not recorded from Scandinavia, Britain, 
<collectingCountry box="[943,1022,1305,1331]" name="Ireland" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Ireland</collectingCountry>
nor the Iberian peninsula; also North Africa. 
<collectingCountry box="[237,336,1341,1367]" name="Portugal" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: three northern provinces.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,1268,1511]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1377,1403]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Ecology.</emphasis>
All Portuguese sampling sites feature canopy by trees and most also open water. Indeed, also in the rest of Europe, the species prefers running water (
<emphasis box="[710,743,1414,1439]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">e.g</emphasis>
., waterfalls, springs) in deciduous forests (
<bibRefCitation author="Pollet, M." box="[1225,1360,1413,1439]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref34362" refString="Pollet, M. (2000) A documented Red List of the dolichopodid flies (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) of Flanders [in Dutch with English summary]. Communications of the Institute of Nature Conservation, 8, 1 - 190." type="journal article" year="2000">Pollet 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,1268,1511]" box="[199,456,1448,1475]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,1448,1475]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
4.6 (rare).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,1268,1511]" box="[199,523,1484,1511]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,1484,1511]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Activity period.</emphasis>
April–June.
</paragraph>
